    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      Newstead has undergone one of the most significant transformations of any Brisbane suburb over the past decade. What was once light industrial land along the river is now one of the city's most desirable inner-city addresses, built around the Gasworks precinct, direct river access and a walkability that genuinely stacks up against anywhere in Brisbane.
    </p>
<!-- APPRAISAL FORM -->
<div style="background:#fff; border-left:4px solid #c4912a; padding:2rem 2rem 1.75rem; margin:2rem 0;">
