<section style="background:var(--color-base, #f2efe9); padding:80px 24px;">
  <div style="max-width:800px; margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#c4912a; margin-bottom:1rem;">FAQ</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); font-weight:300; line-height:1.2; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:2.5rem;">Common questions about Newstead.</h2>
    <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column;">

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What is the median apartment price in Newstead?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Newstead apartment prices vary significantly by building, floor level and view line. Entry-level stock is priced well below riverfront prestige apartments, and premium two and three-bedroom apartments with river views or in quality buildings command a significant premium. The Gasworks precinct proximity and Brisbane River outlook are the strongest price drivers. For a current assessment of a specific property, contact Daniel for a no-obligation appraisal.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          How long does it take to sell an apartment in Newstead?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Well-positioned Newstead apartments with strong views, quality finishes and a good floor plan typically sell within 20 to 40 days. Pricing strategy matters more here than in most Brisbane suburbs, accurate market positioning and targeting the right buyer profile is what separates a campaign that runs too long from one that generates genuine competition.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What is the lifestyle like in Newstead?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Newstead centres on the Gasworks precinct, restaurants, bars, cinema, a Farmers Market on Saturday mornings, and a Harris Farm anchoring the retail offer. The Brisbane River Bikeway runs through the suburb and connects directly to New Farm Park, Teneriffe and the CBD. The lifestyle is urban and walkable, drawing professionals, downsizers and young families who want inner-city access without compromising on amenity.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          Is Newstead a good suburb to sell in right now?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Demand for quality Newstead apartments has strengthened as owner-occupiers, particularly downsizers and professionals, have become a larger proportion of buyers. Properties with genuine river views, large floorplates or in buildings with low body corporate costs continue to attract competitive interest. Investor-grade stock requires a more targeted approach. Speaking with an agent who knows which buildings are performing and why is the most useful first step.</p>
      </details>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

